@notice Uploads a document with its name and IPFS hash
@param name The name of the document
@param ipfsHash The IPFS hash of the document

@notice Shares a document with multiple recipients
@param docId The ID of the document
@param recipients The addresses to share the document with

@notice Retrieves the details of a document
@param docId The ID of the document
@return name Name of the document
@return ipfsHash IPFS hash of the document
@return owner Owner address of the document
@return sharedWithArray List of addresses the document is shared with
@return timestamp Time when the document was uploaded

@notice Adds tags to a document
@param docId The ID of the document
@param newTags The tags to add

@notice Searches for documents by tag
@param tag The tag to search for
@return docIds Document IDs matching the tag

@notice Checks if a user has access to a document
@param docId The ID of the document
@param user The address to check access for
@return True if the user has access, false otherwise

@notice Retrieves all document IDs owned by a specific address
@param owner The address of the owner
@return Array of document IDs owned by the address
